snippet.title: Incunabula DOS Gameplay HD
snippet.description:
A short gameplay video of the 1984 strategy game Incunabula by Avalon Hill. It is the original computerized version of Avalon Hill's Civilization board game and loosely follows the rules of the board game.

If you like the channel, please subscribe and give this video a thumbs up and check out the channel for more retro gaming longplays / playthroughs.

Played by: GameOver

#retrogaming #civilization #retrogames
